{%- comment -%}
  Ganguram — Delivery location -> cart attributes config (Phase 2.10A).

  Publishes window.GanguramCartAttributesConfig (localized Ajax cart URLs + the
  cart attribute key names + the optional read-only "Delivering to" summary label),
  then loads the scoped module. The module mirrors the SELECTED pincode/zone (via
  window.GanguramZone, the single source of truth) into Shopify cart attributes so
  the delivery context travels with the cart/order for admin visibility.

  Handoff ONLY: it does NOT autofill or change checkout, does NOT change the
  checkout URL or button behaviour, does NOT change, create or fake any shipping
  RATE, MOV, date-slot or payment, does NOT change product/cart eligibility or cart
  removal/undo, adds NO Google Maps, and never writes localStorage["Zipcode"].
  Phase 2.11D.2 additionally EXPOSES the cart's Quick-Commerce eligibility + location
  to a shipping-rate app (e.g. ShipZip) via cart attributes (ganguram_all_quick_
  commerce / ganguram_delivery_mode_candidates / ganguram_selected_pincode /
  ganguram_delivery_zone) — the app still owns the actual 4-hour rate.
  Fail-open: any Ajax error is a silent console warning and never blocks checkout.
  Privacy: stores only pincode, zone, zone label, a coarse source label and (only
  if already captured as a short safe city/state summary) that summary — never a
  full street address, lat/lng, or place_id.

  Attribute key names are kept here as plain literals (JSON-safe via | json) so they
  are single-sourced and never embed placeholder tokens inside a default string.
{%- endcomment -%}
<script>
  window.GanguramCartAttributesConfig = {
    enabled: true,
    updateUrl: {{ routes.cart_url | append: '/update.js' | json }},
    cartUrl: {{ routes.cart_url | append: '.js' | json }},
    debounceMs: 600,
    summaryEnabled: true,
    summaryLabel: {{ 'Delivering to:' | json }},
    keys: {
      pincode: {{ 'Delivery Pincode' | json }},
      zone: {{ 'Delivery Zone' | json }},
      zoneLabel: {{ 'Delivery Zone Label' | json }},
      source: {{ 'Delivery Location Source' | json }},
      addressSummary: {{ 'Delivery Address Summary' | json }},
      allQuickCommerce: {{ 'ganguram_all_quick_commerce' | json }},
      deliveryModeCandidates: {{ 'ganguram_delivery_mode_candidates' | json }},
      selectedPincode: {{ 'ganguram_selected_pincode' | json }},
      deliveryZone: {{ 'ganguram_delivery_zone' | json }}
    }
  };
</script>
{{ 'ganguram-cart-attributes.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
<script src="{{ 'ganguram-cart-attributes.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
